'''''Queen Sono''''' ni ikinamico yo muri [[Afurika]] yepfo yerekanwa kuri televiziyo yakozwe na Kagiso Lediga yerekanwe kuri Netflix ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020<ref>https://tvline.com/2020/12/01/queen-sono-cancelled-season-2-renewal-reversed-netflix/</ref>.    Uru rukurikirane rukinamo Pearl Thusi, Vuyo Dabula, Sechaba Morojele<ref>https://deadline.com/2020/12/netflix-reverses-renewal-first-african-original-series-queen-sono-1234635711/</ref>,<ref>https://africasacountry.com/2020/05/queen-sono-and-the-troubling-promise-of-netflixs-future-in-africa</ref> Chi Mhende, Loyiso Madinga, Rob Van Vuuren, Kate Liquorish, Khathu Ramabulana, Enhle Maphumulo, Abigail Kubeka, Connie Chiume, Otto Nobela na James Ngcobo na Featuring Mario Diederiks<ref>https://qz.com/africa/1847687/netflix-debut-african-tv-series-queen-sono-renewed-for-season-2/</ref>. <ref>https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/a34880983/netflix-queen-sono-season-2-cancelled/</ref> Nibikorwa bya mbere bya Netflix .  

imaze kurekurwa, yakiriwe neza n'abayireba, bashimye icyerekezo, sinema, uko ibikorwa byakurikiranye ndetse n'ibitaramo<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/27/arts/television/queen-sono-review-netflix.html</ref>, cyane cyane Soi, Dabula na Kubeka, maze bavuga ko ari "igihe cyiza." Ku ya 28 Mata 2020<ref>https://tbivision.com/2020/12/02/netflix-axes-first-african-original-queen-sono-as-cancellations-continue/</ref>, Netflix yavuguruye urukurikirane rwa season ya kabiri<ref>https://www.indiewire.com/2020/02/queen-sono-review-netflix-africa-original-series-1202213890/</ref>.  Icyakora, ku ya 26 Ugushyingo 2020, byavuzwe ko Netflix yahagaritse uruhererekane kubera ibibazo by’umusaruro byazanywe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 <ref>https://www.news24.com/channel/tv/news/queen-sonos-second-season-cancelled-amid-current-trying-times-20201126-2</ref>. 

== Inyandiko ==
''Queen Sono'' akurikira inkuru [[Afurika y’Epfo|y’umukozi w’ibanga wo muri Afurika yepfo]] wihishe ukemura ibibazo by’ubugizi bwa nabi mu gihe akemura ibibazo mu buzima bwe bwite<ref>https://www.onceuponatime.agency/entertainment/work/netflix/queen-sono</ref>.

